The aim of the study was to assess the immunogenicity and safety of Fluzone Quadrivalent influenza vaccine Southern Hemisphere (SH) 2015 formulation in participants aged 18 to 60 years as well as in participants 61 years or older.

 The objectives were: - To evaluate the compliance, in terms of immunogenicity, of the Fluzone Quadrivalent influenza vaccine SH 2015 formulation with the requirements of the European Medicines Agency (EMA) Note for guidance (NfG) CPMP/BWP/214/96 - To describe the immunogenicity of the Fluzone Quadrivalent influenza vaccine SH 2015 formulation - To describe the safety of the Fluzone Quadrivalent influenza vaccine SH 2015 formulation